      "metadata": {
        "title": "Hily Dating App: Meet. Date.",
        "subtitle": "Chat, match with new people",
        "promotional_text": null,
        "description": "On Hily dating app, date as you are. Chat, flirt online and connect with local singles for real. Turns out dating apps work best when you're just... you.\n\nConnecting is exciting on Hily! Just make a dating profile showing your personality\u2014and find someone who matches your energy. Don't know how to start? Use our icebreakers and compatibility checks to help you chat and flirt. No matter if you\u2019re here for something casual or one of the relationship seekers, there\u2019s room for everyone. Exploring and meeting new people always feels fun.\n\nCheck out Hily's top dating features:\n\u2022 Compatibility Quiz to connect on a deeper level\n\u2022 Fun zodiac synastry score to see if your stars align\n\u2022 Profile verification and safety team for confidence in your dating\n\u2022 Personalized icebreakers to chat and flirt like a pro\n\nDating on apps should be fun. Groundbreaking, we know. Use Hily, your style! Get the app, build your profile, chat with local singles, meet up for real \u2013 and get the relationships you\u2019re looking for. Seeking love? Just moved and trying to network? Want to find local friends? Whatever you need, find it here.\n\nDating is not just about romance. It\u2019s also about sharing life, meeting new friends, feeling seen and discovering what you actually want. Something serious? Or maybe something casual? Hily helps you connect with people near you who are smart, kind and intelligent enough to know that real connection starts with being yourself.\n\nStay in touch with us!\n\u2022 Leave your feedback about the app at apps@corp.hily.com\n\u2022 Wondering about safety and privacy? Take a look at our Terms of Service at https://hily.com/terms and Privacy Policy at https://hily.com/privacypolicy\n\nWe want dating apps to be fun again. And we know there's no other way to date and meet people for real than being yourself. So hop on and have fun dating as you are! Are you in the mood to chat or flirt? Get Hily dating app to enjoy the ride on your terms!",
